29/03/2011
TIRANA, Albania -- The main opposition Socialist Party (SP) submitted its list of candidates Monday (March 28th) for the May 8th local elections.
SP mayors ending terms in most major cities will seek-re-election, including Tirana's Edi Rama.
Former Interior Minister and ruling Democratic Party (DP) representative Lulzim Basha will square off against him.
The DP submitted its candidate list at the weekend.
(Shekulli, Balkan Web, Telegrafi, Top Channel - 28/03/11)
